long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sprunki Retake Has A Re-ReTake Now! This is highly anticipated sequel to the Sprunki series, featuring 7 new characters in this mod for Sprunki Retake!

In the Sprunki Retake Deluxe series, you'll encounter many familiar characters from Sprunki, enhanced with innovative twists, making it the ultimate new installment in the Sprunki game series.
